news.headline: JPMorganChase Declares Preferred Stock Dividends
news.summary: NEW YORK, December 13, 2024--JPMorgan Chase & Co. (NYSE: JPM) ("JPMorganChase" or the "Firm") has declared dividends on the outstanding shares of the Firm’s Series CC and HH preferred stock. Information can be found on the Firm’s Investor Relations website at https://www.jpmorganchase.com/ir/news.
